      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its life. The engine starts reliably and runs smoothly, while the transmission provides crisp, dependable shifts. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, showing only minor signs of careful use. The exterior retains a pleasing appearance with a healthy finish, making this a dependable and attractive choice for its next owner.",
