    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a basic set of wheels to get you from A to B? This vehicle has certainly seen some life and shows significant wear both inside and out, but it offers a great opportunity for someone handy or looking for a very affordable entry into car ownership! It\u2019s a well-loved veteran of the road that\u2019s ready for a new owner who appreciates a bargain and doesn't mind giving it some extra TLC.",
