    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and has served as a dependable daily driver for many years. While the engine and transmission remain functional and the car is roadworthy, buyers should be aware of its age; there are noticeable cosmetic blemishes on the exterior and visible wear on the interior upholstery. Mechanically, you may encounter some minor fluid seeps and suspension noise typical for its mileage, but it remains a solid, budget-friendly option for someone needing reliable transportation.",
