    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to an uncompromising standard that transcends the typical pre-owned market. This unit remains in pristine showroom condition, exhibiting a level of preservation rarely seen outside of a private collection. Every surface and mechanical component reflects a legacy of fastidious care, ensuring a driving experience indistinguishable from new. For the discerning buyer who demands nothing short of perfection, this offering represents a singular opportunity to acquire a truly investment-grade asset.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
